    {
      "content": "An Azure subscription or an <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Azure trial subscription<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/pricing/free-trial/)</ept> - This is only required for accessing the Azure portal and not for using Azure AD Connect.",
