      "pos": [
        7391,
        7562
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "SQL Server Express has a 10GB size limit that enables you to manage approximately 100.000 objects.",
      "pos": [
        7563,
        7661
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If you need to manager a higher volume of directory objects, you need to point the installation process to a different version of SQL Server.",
